data.text: And despite bad weather in Hobart we got picked after a two hour delay - otherwise I had to figure out how to manage 14 people for a night - love southwest Tasmania - keep it Wild - no Huts, no development @TassieWild @AndFishers @TasmanianGreens https://t.co/73oY9LCUzc
